        </p>
      </div>
      <button type="button" class="btn ghost btn-small bucket-toggle" data-target="leading-body">
        <span class="bucket-toggle-icon">▼</span> Collapse
      </button>
    </header>

    <div class="bucket-card-body" id="leading-body">
      <div class="layout-two-column">
        <div class="field">
          <label for="decisionMakingWithRisk">
